    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hi @lowfatcode I think you should be able to accomplish what you want by using a custom template for refinementList and then creating a mustache helper (if you use mustache templating). Here's how:\n\nhttps://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/documentation/#helpers\n\nThere's an example on the right part of the page (on desktop) that shows how to create a helper that would change some numerical data formatting.\n\nI do agree that a generic way to do that (modifying template data before sending to template) could be nice.\n\nLet me know how it goes\n",
