    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> I keep finding I'm fighting it so I may end up just building my DOM from scratch anyway, in which case problem solved!\n\nYep we also think that mustache by default can be a limitation for more advanced users and will default to function templates in the next instantsearch iteration (while still providing mustache templates for users willing to use them).\n\nAnd if you use a function for templates then yes: problem solved you can just compute the template data here.\n",
